# Development Variable Configuration

File: `dev.terraform.tfvars`

```hcl id="rgf8r4"
insta_details = {
  vol_siz    = 40
  vol_typ    = "gp2"
  insta_deta = "t3.small"
}
extra_tags = {
  Name = "Own-terra-tfvars"
}
```

## Explanation

This configuration represents the Development environment.

### Development-Specific Configuration

| Parameter     | Value    |
| ------------- | -------- |
| Volume Size   | 40 GB    |
| Volume Type   | gp2      |
| Instance Type | t3.small |

The Development environment uses:

* smaller storage compared to production
* general-purpose SSD (`gp2`) volume type
* slightly larger instance type for testing and development workloads

